text: Bennie Le Sueur (22 March 1917 – 17 August 1994) was an Australian rules footballer who played for the Footscray Football Club and Collingwood Football Club in the Victorian Football League (VFL). == Notes == == External links == * *Profile on Collingwood Forever Category:1994 deaths Category:1917 births Category:Australian rules footballers from Victoria (Australia) Category:Western Bulldogs players Category:Collingwood Football Club players Category:Braybrook Football Club players
